trans-unit.source: Represents one, and only one, of three possible properties of a print queue: <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Location*>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Comment*>, or <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName*>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en, og bare ett, tre mulige køegenskapene trykt: <> </> *>, <> </> *>, eller <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName*>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName*>

trans-unit.source: An object of this class is primarily used as a parameter for one of the overloaded <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A> methods of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer>.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt av denne klassen brukes hovedsakelig som en parameter for en av overbelastede <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>metoder for <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintServer> </xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>

trans-unit.source: This method makes it possible to install a print queue while initializing only one of its three major <xref:System.String> properties.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden gjør det mulig å installere en køen under oppstart av bare én av de tre største <xref:System.String>Egenskaper.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Having three separate overloads of the method is not possible because they would have the same signature and no two overloads of a method can have the same signature.
trans-unit.target: Med tre separate overlastingene av metoden er ikke mulig fordi de har samme signatur og ingen to overlastingene av en annen metode kan ha samme signatur.

trans-unit.source: If you want to install a print queue and initialize two or more of its major string properties, there is another overload, <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>, that substitutes three <xref:System.String> parameters for the PrintQueueStringProperty parameter.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil installere en køen og initialisere to eller flere av egenskapene for overordnede strengen det er en annen overlasting <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>, som erstatter tre <xref:System.String>Parametere for parameteren PrintQueueStringProperty.</xref:System.String> </xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>

trans-unit.source: These parameters are used to set the major String properties in this order: <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName%2A>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Comment%2A>, and <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Location%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Disse parameterne brukes til å angi egenskapene for store streng i denne rekkefølgen: <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName%2A>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Comment%2A>, og <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Location%2A>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Location%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Comment%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use an empty string for a parameter that corresponds to a property you do not want to initialize.
trans-unit.target: Bruk en tom streng for en parameter som samsvarer med en egenskap som du ikke vil starte.

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Classes within the <xref:System.Printing> namespace are not supported for use within a Windows service or ASP.NET application or service.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Klasser i den <xref:System.Printing>navneområdet støttes ikke for bruk i en Windows ASP.NET-program eller tjeneste.</xref:System.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Attempting to use these classes from within one of these application types may produce unexpected problems, such as diminished service performance and run-time exceptions.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å bruke disse klassene fra i ett av disse programtyper kan føre til uventede problemer, for eksempel dårligere tjeneste ytelse og kjøretid unntak.

trans-unit.source: If you want to print from a Windows Forms application, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil skrive ut fra en Windows Forms-program, kan du se den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>navneområde.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the print queue property that is represented.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir verdien for egenskapen køen som er representert.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A> is <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType>, the Name might be "Department Supply Room"; but if the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A> is <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType>, the Name might be "Use only A4 size paper with this printer."
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A>er <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType>, navnet på kan være "Avdeling oppgi plass"; men hvis <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A>er <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType>navnet på kan være "Bruk bare A4 størrelse arket med denne skriveren."</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> with the value of the property.
Gets or sets a value that identifies which of the three possible properties of a print queue is being represented.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som identifiserer hvilke av de tre mulige køegenskapene trykt representeres.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A> method of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer> uses this information to ensure that the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Name%2A> value is assigned to the correct property of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> being installed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>-metoden til et <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer>bruker denne informasjonen til å sikre at den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Name%2A>verdien som er tilordnet egenskapen riktig for den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>blir installert.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Name%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintServer> </xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType"></xref> that specifies the kind of print queue property that is being represented.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType"> </xref> som angir hvilken type køen-egenskap som er representert.
